# The AiZynthFinder stock set + policy model (public USPTO template policy + ZINC stock, ~0.8 GB) are
# fetched once with upstream `download_public_data` and CACHED on the box under
# $FTO_ADMET_ENV_CACHE/aizynth-data (see README). Models/weights/data are NEVER committed (CLAUDE.md 0),
# and the config.yml holds box-absolute paths, so nothing here belongs in git. Ignore any local copy.
aizynth-data/
*.onnx
*.hdf5
*.csv.gz
config.yml

# isolated pixi env (the box-solved lock is committed; the env itself is not)
.pixi/
